neena gupta ( born 4 july 1959 ) is a popular actress in indian commercial cinema , but it is her work with art filmmakers of india , like g. aravindan and shyam benegal that got her recognition as an actress of considerable repute .   she did a guest appearance in the tv series ; shrimaan shrimati .   she also hosted the indian version of the television quiz show the weakest link , kamzor kadii kaun .